name.vi: Cửa hàng đại lý mở rộng

description.en: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ar: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.br: Cria um clone do seu personagem para gerenciar uma Loja Pessoal para você com duração estendida! Clique duas vezes para fechar a Loja. Você recebe o item de volta quando a loja é fechada.
description.cns: 创建一个你的角色替身，可以为你提供更长时间的个人商店管理。双击关闭商店。商店关闭后，你仍拥有该商品。
description.de: Erschafft einen Klon deines Charakters um deinen Shop für eine längere Dauer zu verwalten. Doppelklicke um deinen Shop zu schließen. Du bekommst deine Gegenstände zurück, wenn du den Shop schließt.
description.fi: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fil: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fr: Crée un clone de votre personnage, qui gérera votre Boutique Personnelle pour vous pendant une durée prolongée ! Double-cliquez pour fermer la boutique. Vos objets vous seront rendus.
description.id: Membuat tiruan karakter Anda untuk mengelola Personal Shop untuk Anda dengan durasi yang diperpanjang! Klik dua kali untuk menutup Shop. Anda mendapatkan barang kembali saat Shop tutup.
description.it: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.jp: キャラクターのクローンを作成して、個人商店を運営してくれます。営業期間も拡張されています。ダブルクリックでショップを閉じることができ、アイテムが戻ってきます。
description.kr: 캐릭터를 복사하여 장기간 개인 상점을 관리합니다! 상점을 닫으려면 두 번 클릭하세요. 상점이 닫히면 아이템을 돌려받습니다.

description.ru: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.sp: ¡Crea un clon de tu personaje para administrar una tienda personal para ti con una duración extendida! Haz doble clic para cerrar la Tienda. Recuperarás el objeto cuando se cierre la Tienda.
description.sw: Creates a clone of your character to manage a Personal Shop for you with an extended duration! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.th: สร้างโคลนของตัวละครของคุณเพื่อจัดการร้านค้าส่วนตัวให้กับคุณด้วยระยะเวลาที่นานขึ้น! ดับเบิ้ลคลิกเพื่อปิดร้าน ได้ของคืนเมื่อร้านปิด
description.tw: 創造一個你的複製人來幫你管理個人商店，雙擊可以關閉商店，商店關閉時將會返回物品
description.vi: Tạo bản sao nhân vật của bạn để quản lý Cửa hàng cá nhân cho bạn kéo dài thời gian! Nhấp đúp để đóng Cửa hàng. Bạn nhận lại hàng khi Shop đóng cửa.
